trans-unit.source: Provides a set of <see langword="static" /> methods that extend the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Fornece um conjunto de métodos <see langword="static" /> que estende a classe <see cref="T:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher" />.

trans-unit.source: The methods in this class are defined as extension methods that extend the <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher> class.
trans-unit.target: Os métodos nesta classe são definidos como métodos de extensão que estendem o <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher> classe.

trans-unit.source: This means that they can be called like an instance method on any <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher> object.
trans-unit.target: Isso significa que eles podem ser chamados como um método de instância em qualquer <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher> objeto.

trans-unit.source: Executes the specified delegate asynchronously on the thread that the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher" /> was created on.
trans-unit.target: Executa o delegado especificado de forma assíncrona no thread em que <see cref="T:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher" /> foi criado.
